title: Knight Rider 2008 Swe sub
description:
Mike Traceur a bitter former Army Ranger and failed race car driver, just got a new lease on life, neither he cares for
or wants this chance to make up for his past failings. FLAG wants a new driver, but he is hesitant to join this mysterious
group and doubts this super car or he can make a difference. He's got problems, he's in debt and people want to kill him.
The choice is all too obvious for him and the Knight Industries Three Thousand (K.I.T.T).
